<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Email Verification</title>
</head>
<body>
    <div style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-color: #FFF; color: #000; margin: 0; padding: 0; line-height: 1.6;">
        <table style="width: 100%; max-width: 600px; margin: auto; padding: 20px; border-radius: 10px; border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);">
            <tr>
                <td style="text-align: center;">
                    <h1 style="color: #332941; margin-top: 0;">Hello <%= name %>,</h1>
                    <h3>Welcome to FlagGuessr24!</h3>
                    <p>To complete your signup, please use the following One-Time Password (OTP) within the next <%= minutes %> minutes:</p>
                </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td style="text-align: center; margin-top: 20px;">
                    <div style="background-color: #F8E559; color: #332941; padding: 10px; border-radius: 5px; text-align: center; font-size: 1.2em; width: 200px; display: inline-block;"><strong><%= otp.toString().split('').join(' ') %></strong></div>
                </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td style="text-align: center; margin-top: 20px;">
                    <p>If you did not request this OTP, please ignore this email. Your account's security is important to us.</p>
                    <p>Thank you for choosing FlagGuessr24!</p>
                    <p>The FlagGuessr24 Team</p>
                </td>
            </tr>
        </table>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
